error_description: 在 'sample' 列中，'25 patients' 和 '2 paxienxs' 等存在拼写不一致的问题。'sample' 列中应为 'patients'，而 'paxienxs' 是 'patients' 的拼写错误。'measure name' 列中 'surgery patients who were taking heart drugs called beta blockers before coming to the hospital6 who were kept on the beta blockers during the period just before and after their surgery' 中的 'surgery' 与 'Heart Attack' 等存在重复或格式不一致的问题。'stateavg' 列中 'AL_AMI-7A' 和 'AL_SCIP-CARD-2' 等存在拼写不一致的问题。
